Pre-Deployment Checklist
Follow these steps to ensure the Limitless Nexus deployment is hardened and secure.
Phase 1: Authentication
• [ ] Service Account: Verify the Google Cloud Service Account has Editor access to folder 1bXBaDMH47RafqbOymfBqESnvRkJxzMfr.
• [ ] GitHub Secrets: Add the Service Account JSON to GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_KEY in the repository settings.
• [ ] Apps Script: Update the GITHUB_TOKEN in the Apps Script Project Properties to allow limitlessfreedom to trigger deployments.
Phase 2: Domain Setup
• [ ] DNS: Point A-records for limitlessnexus.com to GitHub Pages IPs.
• [ ] CNAME: Ensure the CNAME file in the repo contains only limitlessnexus.com.
• [ ] HTTPS: Once the DNS propagates, check "Enforce HTTPS" in GitHub Pages settings.
Phase 3: Financial Terminal
• [ ] Cash App: Confirm the $GulfNexus handle is correct for donation routing.
• [ ] Coinbase: Verify the Commerce API key if using custom checkout flows.
• [ ] Limitless Wallet: Sync tmadias@gmail.com BTC/ETH public addresses for the "Receive" triggers.
Phase 4: Verification
• [ ] Run node Ministry/Integration/index.mjs locally to test Drive sync.
• [ ] Perform a test "Star Matrix" cycle to verify telemetry logging to the Apps Script backend.
